{
  "stem": "7458.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As I mentioned, my parents took in three or four families whose houses were burned by the Germans the day they occupied our hometown, so the house was terribly crowded.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Usually it was a family to a room.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was very little space.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] People couldn't go to work in most instances, although the Germans did allow the tanneries to run for a while.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they allowed my father and my brothers to work in the tannery.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we couldn't sell our products.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They liquidated everything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As for children, there was no school at all.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Next door to us, our neighbors also took in several families, including a shoemaker.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, people always need shoes, so he set up a little bench in the house next door to us to make shoes for the Germans, for the Poles.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my parents said, gee, why don't you help him out?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I went in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Every day I would go next door and actually be an apprentice to a shoemaker.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I actually learned how to make shoes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That would occupy most of my time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As for the women, it was a terrible struggle to find food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Starvation was throughout.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You couldn't buy anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't really let you grow very much.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We did have a garden.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I should say that we always had to depend on our chickens and our own cows for milk and eggs and so on.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But during the German occupation, quite often, our Polish neighbors would seize and return most of it over to the-- to them or to the German commandant, so that there was practically no food.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You couldn't buy very much.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
